text: Pia Alonzo Wurtzbach (; born 24 September 1989) is a Filipina-German beauty pageant titleholder, model and actress. She was crowned Miss Universe 2015 on 20 December 2015. She won the title Miss Universe Philippines 2015 at the Binibining Pilipinas 2015 pageant on 15 March 2015. == Personal Life == She was married to Jeremy Jauncey in Dubai, the founder & CEO of beautiful destination. == Pageantry == Pia started joining pageants at the age of 21, and she was the first winner to become a Mutia ti Albay . She became the representative of Albay last Binibining Pilipinas 2013 - 2015. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Miss Universe winners Category:Filipino actors Category:Filipino models Category:German movie actors Category:People from Stuttgart Category:People from Northern Mindanao
